      <p>This page contains download links for spelling checkers for some of the
      most popular office suites that we support. Languages marked with <img alt="BETA"
      src="images/Beta-Stamp.png" height="30"/> are under development and will
      contain known errors and often a very limited lexicon. Use on your own
      risk! See the project pages for further details. See the <a
      href="devinfo.html">developer info page</a> if you want to build your
      speller from source.</p>

